<br>
With the reduction in Left Axe style damage, the destruction (in my opinion) of the level 50 Left Axe style when it would finally have been a nice style, and the increase in Parry viability in RvR I respecced yesterday.<br>
<br>
I'm currently 44/44/44 and will keep people posted on how it is working.<br>
<br>
Grimfaire Wolfsbane<br>
50 Zerk - Rune/Percival <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#c0c0c0><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub79.ezboard.com/blighttanksofdaoc.showUserPublicProfile?gid=hordgalahad>Hord Galahad</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Journeyman</span><br>  Posts: 24<br> <font color=#000000>(6/16/03 7:28 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub79.ezboard.com/flighttanksofdaocfrm3.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=113.topic&index=1>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: I've respecced.</span><hr size=1> You know by not having 50 in axe your main hand/base damage is effected right? <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#ffffff><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub79.ezboard.com/blighttanksofdaoc.showUserPublicProfile?gid=wyldtiger>WyldTiger</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Journeyman</span><br>  Posts: 15<br> <font color=#000000>(6/16/03 8:24 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub79.ezboard.com/flighttanksofdaocfrm3.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=113.topic&index=2>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: I've respecced.</span><hr size=1> He never had 50 in axe to begin with, so his axe styles should not suffer to much if any lose of damage. <p>Lowery's Law<br>
<br>
If it jams, force it. If it breaks, it needed replacing anyway.</p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#c0c0c0><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub79.ezboard.com/blighttanksofdaoc.showUserPublicProfile?gid=kethryndc>Kethryn DC</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Determined Veteran</span><br>  Posts: 203<br> <font color=#000000>(6/16/03 8:27 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub79.ezboard.com/flighttanksofdaocfrm3.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=113.topic&index=3>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: I've respecced.</span><hr size=1> Yes, Hord, I do know this.  Grimfaire was never a front loading damage machine.  He did good damage and could stay in one on one battles a long time because of his parry.<br>
<br>
Now, we'll see what all changes.<br>
<br>
With realm ranks and armor he is 59/59/59.  So its not like he's hurting at all. <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->  <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#ffffff><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub79.ezboard.com/blighttanksofdaoc.showUserPublicProfile?gid=hordgalahad>Hord Galahad</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Journeyman</span><br>  Posts: 26<br> <font color=#000000>(6/16/03 11:07 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub79.ezboard.com/flighttanksofdaocfrm3.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=113.topic&index=4>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: I've respecced.</span><hr size=1> Yeah but then again I have 50/50/28 +15 to all and a mastery of parry 1.<br>
<br>
so <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> <br>
<br>
Honestly So far I've been able to beat everyone that has respected to 2H (i destroy them) or less axe/la for parry (usually a good fight).<br>
<br>
So i can't say for sure what is bettter since I'd be baised. <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->  <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#c0c0c0><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub79.ezboard.com/blighttanksofdaoc.showUserPublicProfile?gid=yllmar>Yllmar</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC="http://webpages.charter.net/yllmar/images/redball.gif" BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Initiate</span><br>  Posts: 2<br> <font color=#000000>(6/16/03 1:00 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub79.ezboard.com/flighttanksofdaocfrm3.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=113.topic&index=5>Reply</a>   <BR><img src=http://webpages.charter.net/yllmar/images/photo.gif WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: I've respecced.</span><hr size=1> There are definately different ideas about whether dual weild or two-handed is better for a spec.<br>
<br>
Do whatever works for you, as you're the one playing your character.<br>
<br>
My spec is 50 left axe, 48 axe, and 32 parry. <p></p><i>Edited by: <A HREF=http://pub79.ezboard.com/blighttanksofdaoc.showUserPublicProfile?gid=yllmar>Yllmar</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC="http://webpages.charter.net/yllmar/images/redball.gif" BORDER=0> at: 6/16/03 1:03 pm<br></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#ffffff><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub79.ezboard.com/blighttanksofdaoc.showUserPublicProfile?gid=kethryndc>Kethryn DC</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Determined Veteran</span><br>  Posts: 210<br> <font color=#000000>(6/25/03 7:40 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub79.ezboard.com/flighttanksofdaocfrm3.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=113.topic&index=6>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: I've respecced.</span><hr size=1> Well, after the housing fiasco is overwith I'll bring ol' Grimfaire back out into RvR some to see how his new template works.<br>
<br>
As it stands; in PvE its a difference between night and day.  He can tank like he did previous to 1.62.  It just takes him longer and he never uses an anytime style.<br>
<br>
I've run the circle in the caldera killing golemns (blue to OJ) without a single stop because I'd use maybe one style per combat and parry or evade everything.  (current modified 59 parry + Dodger 3).   He's once again able to take out red cons solo.  (caldera lords, high oj, low red; umbroods, etc)<br>
<br>
I didn't notice much, if any damage drop off and the increase in defense more then makes up for it.  I've been buffed and had to peel to tank on an icespine in the glacier and managed to tank it down to one hit either way while everyone else works on the other.<br>
<br>
All in all, if I can't have my damage back, I'm happy with the high parry and not getting hit.<br>
<br>
We'll see how it goes when he ventures forth into RvR again.  (not looking forward to getting hit for 200 by sword/shield using armsmen while I hit them for 130 but I'll give it a shot) <p></p><i></i></td></tr></table> </td></tr></table> <table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top"> </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub79.ezboard.com/flighttanksofdaocfrm3.showPrevMessage?topicID=113.topic"> << Prev Topic</a>&nbsp;| <a href="http://pub79.ezboard.com/flighttanksofdaocfrm3.showNextMessage?topicID=113.topic"> Next Topic >> </a><br><br><a self href=http://pub79.ezboard.com/flighttanksofdaocfrm3.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=113.topic&index=6><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/professional/addReply.gif border=0 alt="Add Reply"></a> </td></tr></table><br><table width=95% border=0><td valign="top"> <a href=http://pub79.ezboard.com/flighttanksofdaocfrm3.emailToFriend?topicID=113.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/image/email.gif border=0 alt="Email This To a Friend"> Email This To a Friend</a><br> <a href=http://pub79.ezboard.com/flighttanksofdaocfrm3.threadControl?topicID=113.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/slate/deleteThread.gif border=0 alt="Topic Control Image"> Topic Commands</a><br> <a href=http://pub79.ezboard.com/flighttanksofdaocfrm3.subscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=113.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/ultimate/subscribe.gif width=20 height=20 border=0 alt="Click to receive email notification of replies"> Click to receive email notification of replies</a> <br>  <a href=http://pub79.ezboard.com/flighttanksofdaocfrm3.unsubscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=113.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/ultimate/unsubscribe.gif width=20 height=20 border=0 alt="Click to stop receiving email notification of replies"> Click to stop receiving email notification of replies</a> <br> </td><td align="right" valign="top"></td></tr><tr align="right"><td colspan=2>